SUMMARY:2nd Annual Crystal Lake Disability Pride Event
DESCRIPTION:Celebrating the beauty\, diversity\, and lived experiences of people with disabilities. Live musicians & singers\, community vendors\, essential community resources\, and more. Fully accessible venue with ASL interpreters\, sensory-friendly quiet zones\, and ADA-accessible parking.\n\nOrganized by Z Advocacy NFP.\nhttps://crystallakedisabilitypride.org
LOCATION:McHenry County College Building B\, 8900 US-14\, Crystal Lake\, IL 60012
URL:https://crystallakedisabilitypride.org
